data.description: This home has been well taken care of and is now in need of a new owner. This home features 2 1/2 baths, a formal sitting area, a formal dining area, and a basement the extends the entire length of the home. The basement could be used for many things such as a man cave, game room, storage or possibly another bedroom or two.Seller allowance of $10,000 to buyer at closing to assist with closing or updates.
